                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "76f829ac-3db3-4b97-a46b-e82f21566dd9",
                            "text": "Examine the Wreath",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.playAnimation",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "animationName": "KneelDown",
                                    "wait": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "16ee1c73-e075-4247-bf02-f11da61f2f09",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Interesting, this wreath hasn't been here very long. It's just starting to dry out and it's not covered with a layer of dust.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "fcc593fa-7706-4124-99fb-711d65f528fd",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "There's a tag on the wreath that says, \"To my beloved brother Donal - May you be at peace. - Shamus.\"",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7b4e7a3c-76d3-471f-bcde-8b3b0a215f0c",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Huh. So my uncle recently brought this here for my father. Maybe for the Nights of the Dead...",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.playAnimation",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "animationName": "KneelUp",
                                    "wait": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ecb91890-bc89-4ed3-912a-abff05091600",
                            "text": "Steal the Wreath",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "08d28e4d-520d-43e3-ac43-c421f2c3f9dc",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Right. Steal something from a Thief memorial. That would be ironic. It would also be moronic - carrying a stolen wreath around the Catacombs.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
